            <text x="256" y="118" font-family="Inter" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="#E67E22">YourProduct Pro"</text>
            <text x="310" y="170" font-family="Inter" font-size="10" fill="#059669" text-anchor="middle">One clear answer</text>
            
